thing.<br /><br /><blockquote id="quote"><font size="1" face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" id="quote">quote:<hr height="1" noshade id="quote"><i>Originally posted by UsulDaNeriak</i><br /><br />thank you very much for your contribution and starting this very senseful discussion on the necro board, we waited for since ages.<br /><br />i am soo surprised and shocked about these bad news.<br /><br />perhaps, we should move this thread to "Newbie Land" and make it sticky. No Necromancer should miss this worthful information.<br /><br />Usul<br /><hr height="1" noshade id="quote"></font id="quote"></blockquote id="quote"><br />Dammit usul you're so mean <img src="images/icon_smile_shock.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="" title="" align="middle" /></span id="msg"></font></td>
